      "columns": ["Type of Fee", "Amount", "Due Date", "Remarks"],
      "rows": [
        ["CFF (Royalty)", "5.9% of Gross Sales", "Weekly (Thursday for 7-day period ending Saturday 12 days prior)", "Note 1, 2"],
        ["CAF (Advertising)", "5.0% of Gross Sales (2.5% for SDOs)", "Weekly with CFF", "Note 3"],
        ["Center Annual Subscription", "$340/restaurant", "Annually", ""],
        ["Additional Training Fee", "$4,000/person", "Upon registration", "If retraining required"],
        ["Training Cancellation Fee", "$1,000 (8-14 days) / $2,000 (≤7 days)", "Upon demand", ""],
        ["Site/Kitchen Layout Design Fee", "$1,200 PSL / $750 PKL (remodel)", "Upon request", "PSL for drive-thru only"],
        ["Inspire Payment Services", "Varies", "Varies", "Billing/admin service fee"],
        ["Loyalty Program Contribution", "1.4% of Loyalty Program Sales (1.2% from 2027)", "Weekly with CFF", "Note 4"],
        ["Taxes", "Varies", "Upon demand", "Reimburse taxes on franchisor fee receipts"],
        ["Late Fee/Interest", "1.5%/month or max legal rate", "Upon demand", ""],
        ["Renewal Fee", "Varies", "Upon signing renewal FA", "Then-current renewal fee"],
        ["Relocation Fee", "Varies", "Upon request", "IFF minus remaining-term credit"],
        ["Insurance", "Cost of obtaining", "As incurred", "Franchisor may obtain at franchisee expense"],
        ["Indemnification", "Varies", "Upon demand", "Claims/liabilities relating to Restaurant"],
        ["Transfer Fee (<3 yrs)", "$12,500 Dunkin' / $20,000 Combo", "Upon transfer", "Note 6"],
        ["Transfer Fee (≥3 yrs)", "$12,500 + $5K-$20K (Dunkin') / $20K + $12.5K-$27.5K (Combo) based on trailing 12-mo GS", "Upon transfer", "Note 6"],
        ["Fixed Documentation Fee", "$2,000/transferee", "Upon transfer", "Non-controlling transfers only"],
        ["DA Transfer Fee", "$10,000", "Upon transfer", "Majority interest"],
        ["Enforcement Expenses", "Varies", "Upon demand", "Successful enforcement of FA/DA"],
        ["Supplier Testing", "$1,000-$10,000", "Upon request", "Testing unapproved supplier samples"],
        ["Lease Costs", "Varies", "Per lease", "If leasing from affiliates; net-net-net"]
      ],
      "table_notes": [
        "Note 1: All fees non-refundable; may be waived/reduced at sole discretion. Gross Sales excludes stored value card deposits, taxes collected, inter-franchisee resale.",
        "Note 2: Standard CFF 5.9%. Incentive programs: Standard ($125K CFF credit, reduced CAF 2%→5% over 4 yrs), Strategic ($225K CFF credit, CAF 2.4%→5% over 9 yrs), Pacific NW ($25K + $50K one-time + $300K 2026-2027 opening credit), Early Opening (0% CFF to required opening date, up to 6 months), VetFran ($10K/restaurant up to $100K).",
        "Note 3: CAF 5.0% standard; 2.5% for SDOs. Standard incentive reduces CAF: 2% yr1, 3% yr2, 4% yr3, 5% yr4+. Strategic: 2.4% yr1-5, 3.4% yr6-8, 5.0% yr9+.",
        "Note 4: Loyalty Program Sales = Gross Sales to Loyalty Program members for in-store eligible products. Reimbursement at NAPC for redeemed items. Fund audited annually by independent third party.",
        "Note 6: Transfer fee based on trailing 12-month Gross Sales tiers: <$400K=$5K/$12.5K, $400-600K=$6K/$13.5K, $600K-1M=$8K/$15.5K, $1-1.4M=$12K/$19.5K, ≥$1.4M=$20K/$27.5K.",
        "Note 8: Lease from affiliates: fixed rent + potential percentage rent; net-net-net structure (taxes, insurance, maintenance, CAM, utilities)."
      ]
